01         Comeback                         September 25, 2017
        The series tells the story of FBI agent Emily Byrne (Stana Katic) who, while hunting one of Boston's most notorious         serial killers, disappears without a trace and is declared dead. Six years later, she is found in a cabin in the woods,         barely alive and with no memory of the years she was missing. Returning home to learn that her husband (Patrick Heusinger)         has remarried and her son is being raised by another woman, she soon finds herself implicated in a new series of murders.


